name: The CUSTOMIZED ¨Oh Darling, How CHARMING¨ bracelet
description: Frassy loves Charm Bracelets, almost more than hearts. We make bracelets customized just for you. What charms, what length, silver/gold chain. You choose. This is our Sample bracelet. They are all homemade so no two products can ever be the same. To purchase, simply Add to Cart and pay. After receiving all your forms back, expect about a week for making and shipping it. A customized charm bracelet for 9 pounds? A Frassy BARGAIN, we believe! Dissatisfied customers- MONEY BACK GUARANTEED. 10% DISCOUNT for all Durham University Students. Be Fresh Funky FRASSY.
